lenders.loan_because:
Giving money to the causes that really matter to the people that benefit from the support are the ones that really motivated me to make an account on Kiva and start lending as soon as I could. I also love the idea that I can give financial support to someone that will use the money to build something new, pay me back and then I can use that money to once again support someone else that wishes to start something new themselves. This is the process that excites me so much about the amazing one of a kind service that Kiva offers the global community.

I am truly inspired by their wisdom and conscientiousness. I aim to do something in my life that can have even a sliver of the impact that the folks that launched Kiva have made. Truly they are an inspiration to me in every aspect of my life.
